{"tid":1636973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阻你地一分鐘，想你地入黎睇睇文宣有幾重要！","createTime":"2019-10-08T00:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T09:05:07.000Z","uid":77702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f150043cadddfd4b38369c8a344b245d823e881","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:41:34.000Z","msg":"首先我想講我係和理非，無論勇武做乜，點裝修都好 我都唔理唔割。因為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地分工要清晰！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非除左出黎行遊行之外，文宣係好重要！但依個亦正正係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地依一個月缺少既野。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n好啦，文宣重要性，我諗基本既係出邊既post 都睇到，我都廢事重覆啦，即係好似宣傳活動之類。<br />\n<br />\n我主要想講既係文宣既重要性在於<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">減低官媒，狗講話既公信力。依一點係不論本土定國際戰線都好重要。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解呀？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老一輩既人，外國人士佢地一定係透過主流電視台 政府官方消息去得到運動既最新狀況</span></span>！而政府就正正用依個優勢去打擊我地呀。假新聞，段章取義既新聞，狗扮示威者等等 再配合埋停狗鐵 好似造成到示威者因為暴力行為而嚴重影響市民日常生活，令到依家既本土同國際聲音開始有啲動搖！<br />\n<br />\n咁我地點做呀？<br />\n<br />\n當然就係要用大量文宣，例如狗扮示威者，將段章取義既新聞成條片post 返出黎，將狗講既大話全部用真實證據俾全世界知佢地係講大話，從而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">減低佢地既可信性，公信力！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後想講多次，和理非勇武要分工，勇武做乜都會係背後支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932b6f0b377454b1ab2b92316ff3c0b635c8fde3","tid":1636973,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:42:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成街都見唔到一個人戴口罩<br />\n如果連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話反抗</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YppYO6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYppYO6J.jpg&h=cb69a584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？"},{"pid":"5183356e431c02e8e67073ea73afa21d83f8b5d3","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:43:13.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要"},{"pid":"286d75a0e2be6804d0f52cf57aca636763784222","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:43:24.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要"},{"pid":"bc9838c9d82e1ef6064098ca5c9881e5fd043f02","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要"},{"pid":"5d166932cc4f8c8b2e00efd703eb4f63e816d693","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要4"},{"pid":"ccd5642129bc0e7419e7d1f45b9e71621d4945cd","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要5"},{"pid":"f85caf53fd9891a5532cfe84f8cc8884e366baf8","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:44:17.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要6"},{"pid":"348ab59cea216f32fa1deee5249427a158700f8b","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:44:28.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要7"},{"pid":"75028f88ed7c5421908dcc75bcacca5ac2106a5f","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:44:42.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要8"},{"pid":"cc883d7cc13b3ff2c9fe93fbdc1af4133ccac112","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:44:52.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要9"},{"pid":"1858ea23ffff428eac5a7888bc61a18547686291","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:45:12.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要10"},{"pid":"5d13b0aff45c3397730a479969115d6706cbd46c","tid":1636973,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:45:24.000Z","msg":"推俾人睇文宣好重要11"},{"pid":"7683